query:
INSERT INTO scores (name, email, score, time)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
        ON CONFLICT (email)
        DO UPDATE SET
            name = EXCLUDED.name,
            score = EXCLUDED.score,
            time = EXCLUDED.time
        WHERE
            EXCLUDED.score > scores.score
            OR (EXCLUDED.score = scores.score AND EXCLUDED.time < scores.time)
